ml_tags: In Memory Of Raymond Joseph (Jay) Bogiatto II 1953-2021 "In the end we will conserve only what we love; we will love only what we understand; and we will understand only what we are taught." An educator, wildlife biologist, and duck hunter, Jay loved waterfowl and this viewing platform. He spent  many hours here with CSU, Chico students, researchers, and friends -Baba Dioum
